{"tid":1758451,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"區選後，以行動對香港有信心，我剛剛再買入了這間上環舖!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2019-11-27T05:19:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T13:30:01.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"63e4d02f0e2044a4ef08c2b87c63ef0c94eb2e33","tid":1758451,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T05:19:25.000Z","msg":"區選後，以行動對香港有信心，我剛剛再買入了這間上環舖。<br />\n<br />\n上環禧利街14號地舖連入則閣。原叫價2880萬，成交2000萬，租金6萬，回報3.6%。建築650呎地舖，連入則閣400呎。租客原味煮意 。 <br />\n<br />\n反修例前原本叫價3300萬，2012年高峰時業主要4000萬，現在真係大跌4-5成。<br />\n<br />\n上手業主2008年4月以1188萬買入。持貨11年，賺68%。<br />\n<br />\n我們買入三大原因:<br />\n(1) 此舖位近上環港鐵站，位於傳統中上環食街核心位，利街飯市人流極多。這間舖我們傾了好耐，業主一直好反覆，到了價又話封盤唔賣。可能因為社運加劇，突然又話賣，我們馬上票到買下來。<br />\n(2) 一線食肆靚位，午市白領消費力強，晚市民生客。位置較少受最近社運影響，地舖連入則閣1000呎，每呎兩萬元算好平。回報3.6厘也不錯。約二千萬這條街近年根本無貨。食牌包括埋閣樓(not storage)，極罕有。<br />\n(3) 業權份數2/7。 樓齡52年，大廈7層高， 土地規劃為商業 commercial， 重建商廈地積比率為15倍。連同旁邊矮層大廈，8個禧利街號碼(6至20)地盤面積合共約6000呎，此舖長揸具收購潛力。<br />\n<br />\n反修例前，禧利街一向是約三千多萬的街道舖。 成交比較: 禧利街8號(只得地舖，建築700呎，門窄好多(門闊只得8呎6吋 vs 我們的舖有13呎))，於2012年12月高峰曾成交3068萬。租客Pokeworld，月租68000。2017年11月蝕賣，也要2600萬。<br />\n<br />\n這間舖是我們今年以來買入的第9間舖，社運對舖市影響大，現在積極執平貨中。 逆市買返啲靚位，只要有租客，回報高，中長揸唔怕。💪💪<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/199534830094852/posts/2602637006451277?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F199534830094852%2Fposts%2F2602637006451277%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRHO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=5255372d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/199534830094852/posts/2602637006451277?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"5463a3b0399ccd81b56e4ba64a31cc6d38df4980","tid":1758451,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T05:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3325339cba3586488ac519683882ca3533e99860","tid":1758451,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T05:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b22506e73be193b118751efd6edd6adbdbb74d","tid":1758451,"uid":58317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:10:47.000Z","msg":"冇事嗱？"},{"pid":"48039b5c8566e1bd54fbe59c7bbe4bbae8a28dc2","tid":1758451,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:13:34.000Z","msg":"租比360 囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f99f6ebc9a0052c08e404e4b3efd57a26aa26d","tid":1758451,"uid":29835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:13:51.000Z","msg":"位置較少受社運影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903f9e05859d2013faea06732def1b5e61494038","tid":1758451,"uid":95181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:17:47.000Z","msg":"條撚屌有喺cctvb賣廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5044dca64773d68be385ffdf06d70a359386c188","tid":1758451,"uid":40743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:19:54.000Z","msg":"條友中立得黎有淺黃feel，不過都係中產人物，懶理d人死活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e32189fb7023794d68258587fef590fa28f243","tid":1758451,"uid":40397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:19:58.000Z","msg":"見佢有個新APP,全港AA都可以收到放盤,咁唔使跟大鋪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4dbad4f68a04ab0d5f6a2b54f973685e794942f","tid":1758451,"uid":186789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:22:30.000Z","msg":"佢之前有拍過片講警暴,有D淺黃,不過以佢做緊個行黎講算係敢出聲,個人黎講幾鐘意睇佢SALE野"},{"pid":"138235b1fd7e6da4ad69f9006d64660d2d60cc0f","tid":1758451,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88dec932677d6f2ac716f2fb1f20a8d4012b95c5","tid":1758451,"ui